        <num>CCP 643</num>
        <heading>643.  Solidary obligees and obligors; joinder</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 643.  Solidary obligees and obligors; joinder
One or more solidary obligees may sue to enforce a solidary right, and one or more solidary obligors may be sued to enforce a solidary obligation, without the necessity of joining all others in the action.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112202</p>
        </authorialNote>
